    <stitle>7 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS FULLER SERIES - REMOVE - COMPANION FLANGE OR YOKE</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="2">
        <title>COMPANION FLANGE OR YOKE</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Lock the transmission by engaging two mainshaft gears (inset,
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302508">Figure 8</hotlnk>). Use a large breaker bar to turn the nut from the output
                shaft.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302508" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302508" filename="../figg13/G1302508.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 8. Lock Transmission and Turn Nut From Output Shaft</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the yoke and speedo gear or spacer from the output shaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302509">Figure 9</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302509" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302509" filename="../figg13/G1302509.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 9. Remove Yoke and Speedo Gear or Spacer</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
